user.description:
You just got FLUSHED by the toilet!

Some poetry: 
I am a toilet, you know what I do
I only eat players who remind me of poo!
As that is my duty, this fact remains true
The ideal dinner for me would be you!
-The toilet
user.about:
Roses are red, violets are blue
A face like yours belongs in a zoo
But don't be mad, I'll be there too
Not in a cage, but laughing at you!
-The toilet
